## Cowork Automation

See `/docs/cowork/` for task templates:
- `research-before-code.md` — Query NotebookLM before implementing features
- `notebook-sync.md` — Sync recent doc changes to notebooks
- `debug-with-notebook.md` — Debug with NotebookLM knowledge base

---

## Tool Profiles

- **minimal** (5 tools) — ask_question, list_notebooks, get_health, setup_auth, list_sessions
- **standard** (10 tools) — adds content generation and source management
- **full** (40 tools) — all tools including audio studio, research, CRUD

Set profile: `npx notebooklm-mcp config set profile standard`
